<title>Add or remove a contact</title>

  <p>To add a contact:</p>

  <steps>
    <item>
      <p>Press the <gui style="button">+</gui> button in the top-left corner
      of the window.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>In the <gui>New Contact</gui> dialog, enter the contact name and their
      information. Click on the drop-down box next to each field to choose the
      type of detail, and fill in the values.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Press <gui style="button">Add</gui>.</p>
    </item>
  </steps>

  <p>To delete a contact:</p>

  <steps>
    <item>
      <p>Select the contact from your contact list.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Press the menu button in the top-right corner of the window and
      select <gui style="button">Delete</gui>.</p>
    </item>
  </steps>

